-- Two Russian `Deep-Cover' Spy Suspects Denied Bail at Hearing in New York
-- David Voreacos
-- 2010-07-01T22:44:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-01/two-russian-deep-cover-spy-suspects-denied-bail-at-hearing-in-new-york.html

          
          
                  July 1 (Bloomberg) --Two of three people accused of
belonging to a “deep-cover” Russian spy ring were denied bail
today by a U.S. judge who agreed with prosecution arguments that
they might flee if released before trial.  
